               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380820-name-744" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-744" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-744" type="surname" value="TIERNEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-744" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MARY TIERNEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of James Tierney, and live in May's-buildings—the prisoner was my servant, and slept in the same room with me and my husband—I carry out milk. On the Saturday night, the 28th of July, I got a sovereign—I put it into my purse, in my pocket—I put my pocket into the tick under my feet—I got up at five o'clock in the morning—I put my hand into my pocket in Orchard-street, and then found the purse—something struck me to look into it, and my sove<lb></lb>reign was gone—I came home, and said to the prisoner, "I Have lost a</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183808200118"></xptr>
               <p>sovereign"—she said, "You don't say so"—I said, "I do"—I sent my little girl for the policeman, and he took her.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380820-name-745" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-745" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-745" type="surname" value="NOBLE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-745" type="given" value="SOPHIA"></interp>SOPHIA NOBLE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am searcher at the station. The prisoner was brought to the station—I found the sovereign in her pocket—she said, "Oh dear what a bad girl I am"—I said, "You are, if you have stolen it"—she said, "I have."</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. I thought it was a shilling.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
